Package: RHRVEasy
Title: Simplified statistical analysis of Heart Rate Variability data 
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: c(person("Abraham", "Otero",
                      email = "aotero@ceu.es",
                      role = c("aut", "cre")),
          person("Constantino A.", "Garcia",
                            email = "constantino.garciama@ceu.es",
                            role = c("aut")),
          person("Sofía", "Bardají",
                              role = c("aut")),
          person("Pablo", "Pérez-Tirador",
                              role = c("aut")))
Description: Runs time-based analysis, frequency-based analysis and non-linear analysis
  of Heart Rate Variability data with the aim of performing a statistical comparison 
  between several groups (e.g., control and treatment). The user just needs to specify
  the path to the groups' data files.
